<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="80" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="80">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="80">On PDA, cultures are initially white, becoming dark orange after 2 weeks. The colonies are flat with irregular edge; texture uniform, producing concentric circles within 1 month at 25 °C in the dark.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
